inner assessment of the values that I give to the needs.

23:32.500 --> 23:39.500
Therefore, if I want to better understand the potential of my needs,

23:39.500 --> 23:42.500
what I want to achieve and why I want to achieve it,

23:42.500 --> 23:46.500
I must start from the component of freedom of activity

23:46.500 --> 23:50.500
and from the category of the value of the needs.

23:50.500 --> 23:54.500
This is what concerns the potential of the needs.

23:54.500 --> 23:56.500
And from the point of view of the Rotor,

23:56.500 --> 24:00.500
based on this formula, I can already assess the potential of the needs.

