25:05.500 --> 25:09.500
is not so much the theory of social learning,

25:09.500 --> 25:14.500
which is well known by specialists who often use it,

25:14.500 --> 25:16.500
not so much its theory of needs,

25:16.500 --> 25:19.500
which, again, is known by specialists who use it,

25:19.500 --> 25:21.500
who use it, who use it,

