57:14.500 --> 57:17.500
hypotheses of the person who owns them.

57:17.500 --> 57:20.500
It makes no sense to ask what constructs are correct.

57:20.500 --> 57:23.500
If these constructs are able to adapt a person

57:23.500 --> 57:26.500
to the surrounding reality,

57:26.500 --> 57:29.500
make him successful in it,

57:29.500 --> 57:32.500
achieve the goals that are before him,

57:32.500 --> 57:35.500
then his constructs are true for him

57:35.500 --> 57:38.500
and useful for him.

57:38.500 --> 57:41.500
It doesn't mean that the same constructs

57:41.500 --> 57:44.500
should be in another person's hands.

57:44.500 --> 57:47.500
If he adapts these constructs,

57:47.500 --> 57:50.500
